                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17891028-14-off68 t17891028-14-cd69"></join>, a pair of silver shoe buckles, value 21 s.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t17891028-14-victim181" type="victimName">
                     Thomas 
                     Smith
                  <interp inst="t17891028-14-victim181" type="surname" value="Smith"></interp>
